{"tid":2176780,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蓮塘開幕　林鄭：(香港穿窿)邊境特特區　明年動工　2025年能進駐","createTime":"2020-08-27T09:49:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-27T13:44:06.000Z","uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3506fe90054ea9fdec916b57271a3215fe004626","tid":2176780,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T09:49:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/truthmediahk/posts/3260351244032374\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftruthmediahk%2Fposts%2F3260351244032374&d=a8feNXbjtso6d%2BC97Zvpk7tFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=f668a0c3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/truthmediahk/posts/3260351244032374</a><br />\n<br />\n【蓮塘/香園圍口岸是日啟用 林鄭：全力支持港深創科園發展】<br />\n<br />\n蓮塘/香園圍口岸是日啟用，貨運設施下午四時開始讓跨境貨車使用，暫時未開放客運服務。<br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥出席開幕式時指政府正全力支持港深創科園發展，並預料明年能於落馬洲河套區供地，預計租戶最快從二零二五年初能進駐。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wub7fjy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwub7fjy.png&h=63c9336a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e7eaffae770d9f4c6d6cccd68a24c2a50d222f1e","tid":2176780,"uid":80503,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T09:52:04.000Z","msg":"林鄭連戲都唔交<br />\n賣港賣到底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c3ff1c51183261348d1ee2bee28f40eba769b62","tid":2176780,"uid":25794,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"e7eaffae770d9f4c6d6cccd68a24c2a50d222f1e","tid":2176780,"uid":80503,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T09:52:04.000Z","msg":"林鄭連戲都唔交<br />\n賣港賣到底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T09:53:54.000Z","msg":"仲起關口即係搞港獨<br />\n建議要拆關"},{"pid":"ea6a690aef2c93ac3a2b1f931c13f4e38bb0ea14","tid":2176780,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T13:34:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji